data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath home on corner lot in Waterstone!  This home features an open floor plan and lots of upgrades to include energy efficient spray foam insulation, granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, 40-year rated architectural shingled roof, prewired for security system, Low-E energy efficient double pane windows & more!  Formal Dining Room is at the front of the house & connects with the Greatroom which is spacious & features a wood burning fireplace with TV mounted above (which remains); Kitchen is fully equipped with breakfast bar, pantry, smooth top electric range, microwave & dishwasher; Laundry room between the kitchen & garage! Master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with his/her sinks, garden tub, separate shower & walk in closet; Guest bedrooms are all good sized and share the guest bath which is located on the opposite side of the house and has double sinks;  Step outside and enjoy the screened porch that overlooks the huge privacy fenced back yard! Double garage with built in doggy doors to back yard.  Located just past Pine Level Elementary School off of Hwy 31.
